avefunction of the scalar (or sound) sector in the hydrodynamic limit directly\nfrom the wavefunction of the vector (or shear) sector, which is usually easier\nto be found because the perturbation wave equations for the vector sector are\nmuch simpler than the ones for the scalar sector.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Sep 2019 16:48:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 May 2020 13:38:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-27"}
