elations\nbetween the FAA and FBA time courses and the LA BOLD activity were\nsignificantly enhanced during the rtfMRI-EEG-nf task. The experimental group\nparticipants reported significant mood improvements after the training. Our\nresults suggest that the rtfMRI-EEG-nf may have potential for treatment of MDD.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Sep 2019 15:47:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Jun 2020 15:30:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-06"}
